The evidence with the title 'Meet the press transcript - july 20, 2014 - NBC News ' says Jul 20, 2014  ... The defense minister , so-called, self-appointed, of the People's Republic Of Donetsk , mr. Igor Strelkov, actually posted a bragging statement on the social media about having shot down a transport . And then, when it became apparent it was civilian , they quickly removed that particular posting. 
